song_lyrics: Nav kanj lochan, kanjmukh, karkanj padkanjāruṇam...
Kandarp agaṇit amit chhabi, nav nīl nīrad sundaram
Paṭ pīt mānhu taḍit ruchī shuchī naumi janak sūtā varam... 1
Bhaj dīnbandhu dinesh dānav daītyavansh nikandanam
Shir mukuṭ kunḍal tilak chāru udār ang vibhūshaṇam
Ājānu bhuj shar chāpdhar sangrām jit khar dūshaṇam... 3
Iti vadati Tulsīdās Shankar shesh munimanranjanam
Mam hradaykunj nīvās kuru kāmādi khaldal ganjanam... 4
title: Shrī Rāmchandra krupālu bhaj man
